10161476626240373321.jpg\" title=\"201610161476626240373321.jpg\" alt=\"201209181431186580.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476626247313906.jpg\" title=\"201610161476626247313906.jpg\" alt=\"201209181431283821.jpg\" width=\"749\" height=\"471\"/></p><p><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476626254400146.jpg\" title=\"201610161476626254400146.jpg\" alt=\"201209181431554615.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476626260134820.jpg\" title=\"201610161476626260134820.jpg\" alt=\"201209181432111344.jpg\"/></p>',1476626129),(9,'公司新闻','宁波市洞桥镇百梁桥颐康园落成典礼','y','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">公司新闻发布<img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627637570147.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627637570147.jpg\" alt=\"201209181416379781.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627641803291.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627641803291.jpg\" alt=\"201209181416524607.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627645488192.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627645488192.jpg\" alt=\"201209181417034025.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627649416470.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627649416470.jpg\" alt=\"201209181417085055.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627653311750.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627653311750.jpg\" alt=\"201209181417492933.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627657265758.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627657265758.jpg\" alt=\"201209181418161347.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610161476627662406339.jpg\" title=\"201610161476627662406339.jpg\" alt=\"201209181418336542.jpg\"/><br/></p>',1476627476),(10,'公司新闻','董事长百梁桥颐康园落成典礼致词','y','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">尊敬的市区镇领导 尊敬的洞桥镇父老乡亲:</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">早上好!</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 很荣幸在我们的奥运健儿在伦敦挥洒汗水，为祖国赢取了一</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">枚又一枚的奖牌之时，我们也能开启我们洞桥镇的小小一幕。我江</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">黎鋆作为一名普通的实业投资者，今天仅做了我应该做的事，完成</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">一件在２００８年已计划好的一件再普通不过的事。 我感到开心</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">与激动。 回想当年，我存感激。 想当初，我作为洞桥镇工业园区</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">第一家的投资企业得到了政府和父老乡亲的大力支持和鼓励，十余</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">年来，我从无到有，从有到具有一定规模，我心存感激。因为有了</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">感激，我懂得了应该回报社会，更应积极参加公益事业。 尽自己</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">的能力去帮助需要帮助的人，让大家的生活更甜美，这是我的心</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">愿。就是因为有此心愿也得到家庭上下的支持尤其是我太太的支</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">持，从２００３年非典时期第一次捐赠一万元给镇人民医院起一路</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">走来，心甘情愿，无怨无悔，即使在当前欧债危机已经严重影响自</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">己企业正常发展下，仍坚持兑现捐建【颐康园】的承诺。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">【颐康园】是我给百梁桥村老人活动中心起的富有寓意的名字</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">【颐】养天年恭迎福禄寿禧春秋不老</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">【康】娱盛世闲弄琴棋书画日月弥新 祝福老人家，祝福百粱桥</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 36px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); widows: 2; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;谢谢</span></span></p>',1476667197),(11,'公司新闻','宁波江友举行季度消防演习','y','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Verdana; font-size: 14px; line-height: 36px; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240);\">为倡导安全生产，增强消防意识，2011年12月28日公司举行季度消防演习，对全厂职工进行消防知识教育。以讲座的形式宣导消防安全的重要性，并进行现场演练，具体内容包括，紧急疏散、险境逃生、组织疏救、现场灭火等。</span><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610171476667382720150.jpg\" title=\"201610171476667382720150.jpg\" alt=\"201209181500507677.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610171476667387974398.jpg\" title=\"201610171476667387974398.jpg\" alt=\"201209181500597890.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610171476667391858567.jpg\" title=\"201610171476667391858567.jpg\" alt=\"201209181501059319.jpg\"/><img src=\"/upload/image/201610/201610171476667396650367.jpg\" title=\"201610171476667396650367.jpg\" alt=\"20